<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Keşfet - Kütüphane Yönetim Sistemi</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #121212;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        h3, p {
            color: white;
        }

        .card {
            border-radius: 12px;
            height: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

            .card:hover {
                transform: scale(1.03);
                box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            }

        .card-body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .card-text {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .btn {
            margin-top: 10px;
            background-color: white;
            color: black;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background-color: black;
                color: white;
            }

        .explore-container {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .row {
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .col {
            flex: 1;
            margin: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container explore-container">

        <div class="d-flex row">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card text-white bg-primary shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Popüler Kitaplar</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">En çok okunan kitaplara göz atın.</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-light btn-sm">Detaylara Git</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card text-white bg-success shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Yeni Eklenenler</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Kütüphaneye yeni eklenen kitapları keşfedin.</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-light btn-sm">Detaylara Git</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="card text-white bg-danger shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Kategorilere Göz At</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Farklı kategorilerdeki kitapları inceleyin.</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-light btn-sm">Detaylara Git</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
